      "content": "\"Stepping away\" means choosing to stop fighting for a place in a world that doesn't see you, because holding on to that hope is only draining your energy further. It's not about giving up on yourself, but rather on the exhausting effort of trying to be someone you aren't when no one is looking. If the noise is too loud and the effort feels pointless, then resting in that quiet, unobserved state is the only honest way to honor your own exhaustion.",
